Hello, thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Elijah Hayes. How may I assist you today?

Hi, I'm feeling a bit unsure about if I should file a complaint. My name is Rachel Russell.

Thank you for reaching out, Rachel. I'd be happy to help you resolve any concerns. Could you please let me know what seems to be the issue?

The listing for the yacht I was interested in had some discrepancies compared to what I saw in person.

I'm sorry to hear that, Rachel. Could you please specify which discrepancies you noticed?

The length of the yacht was listed as forty feet, but it seemed shorter when I saw it.

I understand how that can be concerning. Could you also provide me with the listing ID so I can look into this further?

Sure, the listing ID is A Y B four five two two.

Thank you for providing that information, Rachel. May I also have your contact number for any follow-up questions?

Yes, my number is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Great, thank you. I'll investigate this matter and get back to you as soon as possible. Thank you for your time, Rachel. Have a great day!
